exports[`changelog > changelog 5.20.0..5.22.0 --format markdown 1`] = `
"## 5.22.0 (2024-11-12)

  🆕 Form - 🆕 Form.Item supports hiding labels. [](https://github.com/crazyair)
  🐞 Form - 🐞 Form removes the div used to expand the error height, wraps errorDom and extraDom with a div, and sets a minimum height for the div. [](https://github.com/hongzzz)
  🐞 Form - 🐞 Fix the problem that \`onValuesChange\` is still triggered when the Form field triggers change but the value does not change. [](https://github.com/crazyair)
  🆕 Form - 🆕 Form supports the focus property in scrollToFirstError when form validation fails. [](https://github.com/nathanlao)
  🆕 Table - 🆕 Table column filter drop-down box supports \`filterDropdownProps\`. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🆕 Table - 🆕 Table \`expandedRowClassName\` supports string . [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  💄 Tree - 💄 Fix the problem of missing padding style for selected nodes in Tree. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🆕 Tree - 🆕 Tree component Token adds \`nodeHoverColor\` and \`nodeSelectedColor\` support. [](https://github.com/zmbxy)
  🆕 Tree - 🆕 Tree adds \`indentSize\` token for custom indent width. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🆕 DatePicker - 🆕 DatePicker supports prefix attribute. [](https://github.com/guoyunhe)
  💄 DatePicker - 💄 Fixed the issue of DatePicker.RangePicker flashing when the mouse moves between cells. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🆕 DatePicker - 🆕 In the \`Input.OTP\` component, add \`onInput\` event to get the value of each user input. At the same time, the relevant documentation has been updated. [](https://github.com/aojunhao123)
  🐞 DatePicker - 🐞 Fixed the problem that Input.OTP cannot specify \`inputMode\`. [-rudzinski](https://github.com/alan-rudzinski)
  🆕 DatePicker 🆕 ColorPicker supports \`disabledFormat\`. [-muzhi](https://github.com/su-muzhi)
  🆕 DatePicker 🆕 Add \`cursor\` configuration item to the \`focus\` method of InputNumber component to control the cursor position. [](https://github.com/aojunhao123)
  🆕 DatePicker 🆕 Cascader adds \`disabled\` attribute to disable all first-level directory items of the component. [](https://github.com/aojunhao123)
  🆕 DatePicker 🆕 Descriptions supports single-line spreading. [](https://github.com/crazyair)
  🆕 DatePicker 🆕 Select/TreeSelect/Cascader components add \`prefix\` property to support custom prefix. [](https://github.com/guoyunhe)
  🐞 DatePicker 🐞 Fix the problem that the preview image class name is lost when setting \`ImageProps.preview.rootClassName\` in Image. [](https://github.com/dislido)
  🐞 DatePicker 🐞 Fixed the issue that the last item in the TimePicker panel column cannot be scrolled to the top. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 DatePicker 🐞 Fix TreeSelect dropdown height not enough. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 DatePicker 🐞 Fixed the issue that Typography is not updated immediately when the ConfigProvider language is switched. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)
  🐞 DatePicker 🐞 Fixed the issue that Upload \`itemRender\` calling \`action.preview\` will cause a crash. [](https://github.com/yoyo837)
  🐞 DatePicker 🐞 Fixed Splitter pseudo-element symbol issue. [](https://github.com/dislido)
  💄 DatePicker 💄 Optimize Collapse accessibility attribute and mouse hover style. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 DatePicker 💄 Fix styling issue of Menu title content. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Upload exports type DraggerProps. [](https://github.com/DBvc)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Add defaultValue property to TimePicker.RangePicker example. [](https://github.com/nathanlao)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Message Optimize the top type in message.config. [](https://github.com/Fog3211)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Optimize the TS definition of Tree and TreeSelect. [](https://github.com/afc163)

## 5.21.6 (2024-10-28)

  🐞 Tree.DirectoryTree 🐞 Fix Tree.DirectoryTree interactive area not being a whole row.
  🐞 the 🐞 Fix the Button icon was not vertically centered.
  🐞 the 🐞 Fix the pointer style not set to \`not-allowed\` in the \`disabled\` state when \`variant\` of the Input was set to \`borderless\`. [](https://github.com/ustcfury)
  💄 Splitter - 💄 Improve the pre-rendered style of Splitter under SSR.
  💄 Splitter - 💄 Increased the click area of ​​the Splitter collapse button to improve usability. [](https://github.com/aojunhao123)
  💄 Splitter 💄 Improve Checkbox \`indeterminate\` to enhance accessibility experience. [](https://github.com/SpaNb4)
  💄 Splitter 💄 Improve the \`title\` of the Empty preset svg image to improve accessibility experience.

## 5.21.5 (2024-10-21)

  🐞 Cascader 🐞 Fix Cascader filter limitation not working when \`limit\` set to \`false\`. [](https://github.com/dongbanban)
  🐞 DatePicker 🐞 Fix DatePicker disabled items cannot response mouse events bug. [-mparticle](https://github.com/ajenkins-mparticle)
  🐞 FloatButton 🐞 Fix FloatButton menu problem what is difficult to click. [](https://github.com/aojunhao123)
  🐞 QRCode 🐞 Fix QRCode \`onRefresh\` property not working properly. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🐞 Typography 🐞 Fix Typography links cannot be selected by user. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)
  💄 Badge 💄 Fix Badge incorrect token of texts. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  💄 Layout 💄 Fix Layout lost styles of collapse button. [](https://github.com/aojunhao123)
  🆕 Button 🛠 Improve Button event handler declaration. [](https://github.com/SohaibRaza)
  🆕 Splitter 🛠 Improve Splitter style token semantic name. [](https://github.com/wanpan11)

## 5.21.4 (2024-10-14)

  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed Input.Search not applying the \`hoverBorderColor/activeBorderColor\` token for hover/active states. [](https://github.com/iqingting)
  🐞 Tree 🐞 Fix Tree icon align issue. [](https://github.com/Meowu)
  🐞 Splitter 🐞 Fix Splitter occasionally shows unnecessary scrollbars in nested combinations. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  💄 General 💄 Modify Button \`textHoverBg\` hover background to \`colorFillTertiary\`. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Improve type of Switch \`eventHandler\`. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)

## 5.21.3 (2024-10-09)

  💄 General 💄 Added a scroll bar to Dropdown when having many items. [-Asdf](https://github.com/Cameron-Asdf)
  🐞 Slider - 🐞 Fix Slider issue where the \`id\` prop is not supported.
  🐞 Slider - 🐞 Fix Slider to address the issue causing \`useLayoutEffect does nothing on the server\` warning when \`extractStyle\` is invoked.
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix ColorPicker with gradient mode, sometimes handle color will be force sync back to first handle color issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Table 🐞 Fix Table \`onChange\` function receiving incorrect sorter value. [](https://github.com/nathanlao)
  🐞 Splitter - 🐞 Fix the issue about throw a warning when Splitter nested in a hidden tab panel. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🐞 Splitter - 🐞 Fix the issue about Splitter had unexpected gaps in Flex. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🐞 Splitter 🐞 MISC: Restore \`react\` and \`react-dom\` peerDependencies. [](https://github.com/chentsulin)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Improve type of Slider \`eventName\`. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)

## 5.21.2 (2024-10-01)

  🐞 Typography 🐞 Revert to fix Typography \`copyable\` icon align issue. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Tabs 🐞 Fix Tabs flicker when browser zoom is enabled. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Select incorrect \`activeBorderColor\` token when variant is filled. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed Input.Search alignment issue between the input field and search button at different zoom levels. [](https://github.com/nathanlao)
  💄 General 💄 MISC: Tweak outline width of focus style from \`4px\` to \`3px\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Splitter - 🐞 Fixed the issue with Splitter dragging abnormally on touch screen devices. [](https://github.com/sakuraee)
  💄 Splitter - 💄 Fixed Splitter.Panel style is invalid error. [](https://github.com/wanpan11)
  🗑 Splitter ⚡️ Remove TransButton in Table/Transfer/Typography. [](https://github.com/afc163)

## 5.21.1 (2024-09-25)

  🐞 Button 🐞 Fix Button issue where \`type="link"\` incorrectly used \`colorPrimary\`. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🐞 Button 🐞 Fix Button style class name weight issue that caused custom gradient styles to be overridden. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🐞 Transfer 🐞 Fix Transfer width issue when customized as TableTransfer. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)

## 5.21.0 (2024-09-22)

  💄 Button - 💄 Button adds \`textColor\`, \`textHoverColor\` and \` textActiveColor\` tokens. [](https://github.com/madocto)
  🆕 FloatButton - 🆕 FloatButton supports \`placement\` property, allowing menus to pop up from multiple directions. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 FloatButton - 🆕 FloatButton supports \`htmlType\` prop. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  💄 FloatButton - 💄 Unify FloatButton and FloatButton.Group button round style. [](https://github.com/Layouwen)
  💄 FloatButton - 💄 Manage FloatButton's \`z-index\` with \`useZIndex\` to improve compatibility with other popup components. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 Menu - 🆕 Menu.Item and Dropdown's \`menu\` supports \`extra\` prop now. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🐞 Menu - 🐞 Fix Menu \`popupStyle\` not working on SubMenu. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🆕 Table - 🆕 Table supports \`minWidth\` for columns. [](https://github.com/linxianxi)
  🐞 Table - 🐞 Fix Table empty and shadow issues in virtual mode. [](https://github.com/linxianxi)
  🐞 Table - 🐞 Fix Table column selection issue where deselection was not possible under certain circumstances. [](https://github.com/Jarryxin)
  🆕 Input - 🆕 Input.OTP support \`type\` to help handle some case need number only. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Input - 🐞 Fix Select inside Input addon text color when Select is focused. [](https://github.com/DDDDD12138)
  🛠 Modal - ⌨️ Fix Modal throws warning \`avoid using aria-hidden on a focused element or its ancestor\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🆕 Modal - 🆕 Modal supports \`closable.disabled\` prop now. [](https://github.com/Ke1sy)
  🐞 Descriptions - 🐞 Fix Descriptions column is missing in some cases. [](https://github.com/yezhonghu0503)
  🐞 Descriptions - 🐞 Revert to fix the issue where the popup layer component inside Descriptions is being cut off. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🆕 Upload - 🆕 Upload will pass \`name\` prop to \`<input type="file" />\`. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🆕 Upload - 🆕 Upload \`showUploadList.showXxxIcon\` accept a function value now. [](https://github.com/guoyunhe)
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix ColorPicker when type hex input may not get correct color with precision issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Adjust ColorPicker popup panel not lock by \`value\` to allow control mode with \`onChangeComplete\` scenarios. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 App - 🐞 Fixed App warn about \`zIndex\` too large when using the \`modal\` with having popup component method via \`useApp\`. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 App - 🐞 Fix App rtl style does not respect ConfigProvider direction prop. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 Pagination - 🆕 Pagination \`showSizeChanger\` accepts Select props now. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 Pagination - 💄 Remove Pagination default font family. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 Select - 💄 Add more tokens for Select to customize hover/focus style. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🐞 Select - 🐞 Fix Select search text overlap with arrow icon. [](https://github.com/yezhonghu0503)
  🐞 Select - 🐞 Fix Select extra background of clear icon when enable \`allowClear\` and \`variant="filled"\`. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Segmented adds \`vertical\` property and improves accessibility. [](https://github.com/liangchaofei)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Radio.Group supports \`block\` prop now. [](https://github.com/yuanliu147)
  🆕 Select 🆕 ConfigProvider supports configuring the \`className\` and \`style\` properties of the Splitter component. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Image add \`onActive\` to \`toolbarRender\` for toggling images . [](https://github.com/madocto)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Add ref on List component. [](https://github.com/Asanio06)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Collapse support \`classNames\` and \`styles\` for semantic style customization. [](https://github.com/wanpan11)
  💄 Select 💄 Make Skeleton.Node custom node by remove it's default icon children. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Layout.Sider can not modify theme when used alone. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Typography \`copyable\` with array \`children\` has additional \`,\` string issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Tour where long title will overlap with close button. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🛠 Select 🌐 Localization
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Checkbox adds onFocus\` and \`onBlur\` in type definition. [](https://github.com/huiliangShen)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Fix Badge property type definition to support passing mouse events. [](https://github.com/yuanliu147)

## 5.20.6 (2024-09-09)

  🐞 Menu 🐞 Improve Menu collapse animation smoothness. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Table 🐞 Fix Table cell overflow bug if edit with virtual scroll. [](https://github.com/huiliangShen)
  🐞 Input.Search 🐞 Fix Input.Search button radius not changing with \`size\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Form 🐞 Fix Form password still can be toggle show/hide even if disabled. [](https://github.com/Jarryxin)
  🐞 wrap 🐞 Revert to fix wrap behavior for Dropdown, and re-fix wrap when out of screen edge. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 Badge 💄 Fix Badge background transition when mouse out. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Fix Collapse types for \`onChange\` arguments. [](https://github.com/yuanliu147)

## 5.20.5 (2024-09-03)

  🆕 internal 🛠 Adjust Tree & TreeSelect \`defaultExpandAll\` logic to only add internal \`expandedKeys\` which \`treeNode\` has children instead to avoid perf issue when with large data or \`loadData\` case. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Cascader 🐞 Fix Cascader not show parent option in search when using \`multiple\`.
  🐞 Typography 🐞 Fix Typography \`ellipsis.tooltip.title\` with ReactNode will cause dead loop. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)

## 5.20.4 (2024-09-02)

  🐞 Menu - 🐞 Fix Menu token \`itemPaddingInline inoperative\` not working. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🐞 Menu - 🐞 Fix Menu missing \`hover\` transition style. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 Menu 💄 Badge add transition effect to count node. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 Menu 💄 Fix Table column header move with unexpected transition. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🆕 Menu 🛠 Refactor Typography code to optimize internal logic. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Menu 🐞 Disable the Rate component within Form.Item when the form is disabled. [](https://github.com/nikzanda)
  🛠 Menu 🌐 Patch tr_TR \`Transfer.deselectAll\` locale. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)

## 5.20.3 (2024-08-26)

  🐞 Typography 🐞 Refactor Typography native css ellipsis measure logic to handle precision edge case. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix ColorPicker \`onChangeComplete\` not correct when click directly without move on the picker panel. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 FloatButton.Group 🐞 Fix FloatButton.Group with controlled mode warning for nest updating issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)

## 5.20.2 (2024-08-19)

  💄 the 💄 Fix the suffix style problem of InputNumber without control. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 General 🆕 Form \`rule.message\` supports skipping variable substitution through \`\\\\\${}\`. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the issue where the rounded corners of the trigger element are missing when the FloatButton component has shape="square" and in menu mode when the menu pops up. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the problem that Upload.Dragger does not work when dragging and dropping upload folders. [](https://github.com/huiliangShen)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the issue where the arrow icon disappears after hovering when Select specifies \`getPopcontainer={node=node.parentNode}\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the arrow misalignment error when Popover sets the \`arrow.pointAtCenter\` property. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Roll back the Table partial generic constraint object to any to reduce break changes caused by . [](https://github.com/crazyair)

## 5.20.1 (2024-08-11)

  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix ColorPicker compile error of \`-design/fast-color\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 ColorPicker - 💄 Fix ColorPicker not adjust border style when under Space.Compact. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  💄 ColorPicker 💄 Fix Table \`zIndexTableFixed\` token not support CSS var. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix FloatButton don't support \`zIndexPopupBase\` token. [-io](https://github.com/Yuzu-io)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Typography \`tooltip\` not show with precision issue of \`ellipsis\`. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Form \`preserve={false}\` should not trigger \`shouldUpdate\` rerender. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Tour default \`z-index\` not follow \`zIndexPopup\` token issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Calendar \`locale\` should override \`locale\` from ConfigProvider. [](https://github.com/Asanio06)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Spin align issue when setting \`percent\`. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Tree switcher position not ping at top when title break the line. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🛠 ColorPicker 🌐 Locales
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Refine Table all Record types from any to Object. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)

## 5.20.0 (2024-08-03)

  🆕 ColorPicker - 🛠 Replace ColorPicker internal \`/tinycolor\` with \`-design/fast-color\`.
  🆕 ColorPicker - 🆕 ColorPicker support gradient color type and fix controlled mode not working.
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix the issue where line-height is not effective in cssinjs mode for ColorPicker. [](https://github.com/vagusX)
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix cursor disabled state for ColorPicker. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  💄 ColorPicker - 💄 Optimize ColorPicker when selecting a color from the \`transparent\` state, it defaults to using a bright color instead of black color to enhance the user interaction experience.
  🆕 ColorPicker 🆕 ConfigProvider support indicator property for Spin. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 ColorPicker 🆕 Upload \`showUploadList\` support \`extra\` for additional content. [](https://github.com/guoyunhe)
  🆕 ColorPicker 🆕 Tree support custom loading icon for tree nodes with new prop \`switcherLoadingIcon\`. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 Slider - 🆕 Slider support \`range.editable\` to dynamic add/remove handles.
  🆕 Slider - 🆕 Slider \`range.editable\` support \`minCount\` and \`maxCount\`.
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Support custom status render in QRCode. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Table component supports custom Filter dropdown box empty status. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Allow user to add the Divider style of \`dashed\`, \`dotted\` or \`solid\`. [-08](https://github.com/pinaki-08)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 InputNumber supports \`suffix\` prop. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Input/TextArea/Mentions support \`onClear\` prop. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🛠 Slider ⌨️ Optimize Input be changed repeatedly when hold the enter key in multi-mode. [rc-input#72](https://github.com/react-component/input/pull/72/files) [](https://github.com/crazyair)
  🐞 Slider 🐞 Fix grouping columns does not apply sorting for Table. [](https://github.com/Zyf665)
  🐞 Slider 🐞 Fix Popover/PopConfirm/Tooltip with \`topLeft\`, \`topRight\`, \`bottomLeft\`, \`bottomRight\` zoom in transform origin not correct when target element width is too large.
  💄 Slider 💄 Fix Tree filter node style lost. [](https://github.com/wanpan11)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Component Token support string and number. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Improve Radio export types. [](https://github.com/baicie)
  🛠 TypeScript 🌐 Locales"
