  💄 Badge 💄 Fix Badge incorrect token of texts. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  💄 Layout 💄 Fix Layout lost styles of collapse button. [](https://github.com/aojunhao123)
  🆕 Button 🛠 Improve Button event handler declaration. [](https://github.com/SohaibRaza)
  🆕 Splitter 🛠 Improve Splitter style token semantic name. [](https://github.com/wanpan11)

## 5.21.4 (2024-10-14)

  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed Input.Search not applying the \`hoverBorderColor/activeBorderColor\` token for hover/active states. [](https://github.com/iqingting)
  🐞 Tree 🐞 Fix Tree icon align issue. [](https://github.com/Meowu)
  🐞 Splitter 🐞 Fix Splitter occasionally shows unnecessary scrollbars in nested combinations. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  💄 General 💄 Modify Button \`textHoverBg\` hover background to \`colorFillTertiary\`. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
