  🐞 Tabs 🐞 Fix Tabs flicker when browser zoom is enabled. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Select incorrect \`activeBorderColor\` token when variant is filled. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed Input.Search alignment issue between the input field and search button at different zoom levels. [](https://github.com/nathanlao)
  💄 General 💄 MISC: Tweak outline width of focus style from \`4px\` to \`3px\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
