  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix ColorPicker \`onChangeComplete\` not correct when click directly without move on the picker panel. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 FloatButton.Group 🐞 Fix FloatButton.Group with controlled mode warning for nest updating issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)

## 5.20.2 (2024-08-19)

  💄 the 💄 Fix the suffix style problem of InputNumber without control. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 General 🆕 Form \`rule.message\` supports skipping variable substitution through \`\\\\\${}\`. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the issue where the rounded corners of the trigger element are missing when the FloatButton component has shape="square" and in menu mode when the menu pops up. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the problem that Upload.Dragger does not work when dragging and dropping upload folders. [](https://github.com/huiliangShen)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the issue where the arrow icon disappears after hovering when Select specifies \`getPopcontainer={node=node.parentNode}\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 General 🐞 Fixed the arrow misalignment error when Popover sets the \`arrow.pointAtCenter\` property. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Roll back the Table partial generic constraint object to any to reduce break changes caused by . [](https://github.com/crazyair)

## 5.20.1 (2024-08-11)

  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix ColorPicker compile error of \`-design/fast-color\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 ColorPicker - 💄 Fix ColorPicker not adjust border style when under Space.Compact. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  💄 ColorPicker 💄 Fix Table \`zIndexTableFixed\` token not support CSS var. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix FloatButton don't support \`zIndexPopupBase\` token. [-io](https://github.com/Yuzu-io)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Typography \`tooltip\` not show with precision issue of \`ellipsis\`. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Form \`preserve={false}\` should not trigger \`shouldUpdate\` rerender. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Tour default \`z-index\` not follow \`zIndexPopup\` token issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Calendar \`locale\` should override \`locale\` from ConfigProvider. [](https://github.com/Asanio06)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Spin align issue when setting \`percent\`. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🐞 ColorPicker 🐞 Fix Tree switcher position not ping at top when title break the line. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🛠 ColorPicker 🌐 Locales
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Refine Table all Record types from any to Object. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)

## 5.20.0 (2024-08-03)

  🆕 ColorPicker - 🛠 Replace ColorPicker internal \`/tinycolor\` with \`-design/fast-color\`.
  🆕 ColorPicker - 🆕 ColorPicker support gradient color type and fix controlled mode not working.
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix the issue where line-height is not effective in cssinjs mode for ColorPicker. [](https://github.com/vagusX)
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix cursor disabled state for ColorPicker. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  💄 ColorPicker - 💄 Optimize ColorPicker when selecting a color from the \`transparent\` state, it defaults to using a bright color instead of black color to enhance the user interaction experience.
  🆕 ColorPicker 🆕 ConfigProvider support indicator property for Spin. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 ColorPicker 🆕 Upload \`showUploadList\` support \`extra\` for additional content. [](https://github.com/guoyunhe)
  🆕 ColorPicker 🆕 Tree support custom loading icon for tree nodes with new prop \`switcherLoadingIcon\`. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 Slider - 🆕 Slider support \`range.editable\` to dynamic add/remove handles.
  🆕 Slider - 🆕 Slider \`range.editable\` support \`minCount\` and \`maxCount\`.
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Support custom status render in QRCode. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Table component supports custom Filter dropdown box empty status. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Allow user to add the Divider style of \`dashed\`, \`dotted\` or \`solid\`. [-08](https://github.com/pinaki-08)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 InputNumber supports \`suffix\` prop. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🆕 Slider 🆕 Input/TextArea/Mentions support \`onClear\` prop. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🛠 Slider ⌨️ Optimize Input be changed repeatedly when hold the enter key in multi-mode. [rc-input#72](https://github.com/react-component/input/pull/72/files) [](https://github.com/crazyair)
  🐞 Slider 🐞 Fix grouping columns does not apply sorting for Table. [](https://github.com/Zyf665)
  🐞 Slider 🐞 Fix Popover/PopConfirm/Tooltip with \`topLeft\`, \`topRight\`, \`bottomLeft\`, \`bottomRight\` zoom in transform origin not correct when target element width is too large.
  💄 Slider 💄 Fix Tree filter node style lost. [](https://github.com/wanpan11)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Component Token support string and number. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Improve Radio export types. [](https://github.com/baicie)
  🛠 TypeScript 🌐 Locales"
`;

