### 17. BackTop: Removed. Use FloatButton.BackTop instead.

**Search regex:** \`import\\s*\\{[^}]*\\bBackTop\\b[^}]*\\}\\s*from\\s*['"]antd['"]\`

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { BackTop } from 'antd';
<BackTop />
\`\`\`
**After:**
