## Comment

### Removed from antd. Use @ant-design/compatible instead.

**BREAKING** | 📝 manual

1. Install @ant-design/compatible: npm install @ant-design/compatible
2. Change import from 'antd' to '@ant-design/compatible'

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { Comment } from 'antd';
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
