\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { PageHeader } from '@ant-design/pro-components';
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`import\\s*\\{[^}]*\\bPageHeader\\b[^}]*\\}\\s*from\\s*['"]antd['"]\`

**Reference:** https://ant.design/docs/react/migration-v5

## BackTop

### Removed. Use FloatButton.BackTop instead.

**BREAKING** | 🔧 auto-fixable

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { BackTop } from 'antd';
<BackTop />
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { FloatButton } from 'antd';
<FloatButton.BackTop />
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`import\\s*\\{[^}]*\\bBackTop\\b[^}]*\\}\\s*from\\s*['"]antd['"]\`

## message

### Static methods \`message.xxx()\` deprecated. Use \`App.useApp()\` hook instead for context support.

**BREAKING** | 📝 manual

1. Wrap app with <App /> component
2. Use const { message } = App.useApp(); in functional components
3. Replace static message.xxx() calls with the hook-provided instance

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { message } from 'antd';
message.success('Done!');
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { App } from 'antd';
const MyComponent = () => {
  const { message } = App.useApp();
  message.success('Done!');
};
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`\\bmessage\\.(success|error|warning|info|loading|open)\\(\`

### \`message.warn()\` completely removed. Use \`message.warning()\` instead.

**BREAKING** | 🔧 auto-fixable

Search for \`message.warn(\` and replace with \`message.warning(\`.

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
message.warn('Something went wrong');
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
message.warning('Something went wrong');
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`\\bmessage\\.warn\\(\`

## notification

### Static methods \`notification.xxx()\` deprecated. Use \`App.useApp()\` hook instead.

**BREAKING** | 📝 manual

Same pattern as message — use App.useApp() to get notification instance.

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { notification } from 'antd';
notification.success({ message: 'Done!' });
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
import { App } from 'antd';
const MyComponent = () => {
  const { notification } = App.useApp();
  notification.success({ message: 'Done!' });
};
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`\\bnotification\\.(success|error|warning|info|open)\\(\`

### Static method \`notification.close()\` renamed to \`notification.destroy()\`. Static config options restricted.

**BREAKING** | 📝 manual

1. Rename notification.close() to notification.destroy()
2. Static methods no longer allow dynamic prefixCls, maxCount, top, bottom, getContainer in open()
3. Use useNotification hook if you need different configurations

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
notification.close(key);
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
notification.destroy(key);
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`\\bnotification\\.close\\(\`

## Table

### Column \`filterDropdown\` render args changed. \`confirm({ closeDropdown: false })\` replaced by separate \`close\` function.

**BREAKING** | 📝 manual

Update filterDropdown render function signature to use the new \`close\` parameter instead of \`confirm({ closeDropdown: false })\`.

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
filterDropdown: ({ confirm }) => (
  <Button onClick={() => confirm({ closeDropdown: false })}>Filter</Button>
)
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
filterDropdown: ({ confirm, close }) => (
  <Button onClick={() => close()}>Filter</Button>
)
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`filterDropdown.*closeDropdown\`

### Column prop \`filterDropdownVisible\` renamed to \`filterDropdownOpen\`.

**BREAKING** | 🔧 auto-fixable

Search for \`filterDropdownVisible\` in Table column definitions and rename to \`filterDropdownOpen\`.

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
{ title: 'Name', dataIndex: 'name', filterDropdownVisible: visible }
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
{ title: 'Name', dataIndex: 'name', filterDropdownOpen: visible }
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`filterDropdownVisible\`

## Form

### Prop \`labelCol\` and \`wrapperCol\` can now be set globally via ConfigProvider.

non-breaking | 📝 manual

Optional improvement: move repeated labelCol/wrapperCol config to ConfigProvider for consistency.

## Slider

### Tooltip-related APIs converged into \`tooltip\` property. \`tooltipVisible\` → \`tooltip.open\`, \`tipFormatter\` → \`tooltip.formatter\`, etc.

**BREAKING** | 📝 manual

Migrate Slider tooltip props:
- tooltipVisible → tooltip.open
- tipFormatter → tooltip.formatter
- tooltipPlacement → tooltip.placement
- getTooltipPopupContainer → tooltip.getPopupContainer

**Before:**
\`\`\`tsx
<Slider tooltipVisible={show} tipFormatter={(v) => \`\${v}%\`} />
\`\`\`

**After:**
\`\`\`tsx
<Slider tooltip={{ open: show, formatter: (v) => \`\${v}%\` }} />
\`\`\`

**Search pattern:** \`<Slider[^>]*\\b(tooltipVisible|tipFormatter|tooltipPlacement|getTooltipPopupContainer)\\b\`"
`;

exports[`migrate > migrate 4 5 --format text 1`] = `
"Migration Guide: v4 → v5

  Global:
    📝 [BREAKING] Design token system replaces Less variables. All Less variable overrides must be migrated to CSS-in-JS tokens via ConfigProvider.
       Guide: https://ant.design/docs/react/migrate-less-variables
    📝 [BREAKING] Component styles no longer include CSS reset. Wrap app with <App /> component to restore.
       Guide: https://ant.design/components/app
    🔧 [BREAKING] Moment.js replaced by Day.js. All date-related components (DatePicker, TimePicker, Calendar) now use Day.js.
    📝 [BREAKING] babel-plugin-import is no longer needed. antd v5 supports tree-shaking natively.
    🔧 [BREAKING] \`antd/dist/antd.css\` and \`antd/dist/antd.less\` removed. CSS-in-JS generates styles automatically.
    📝 [BREAKING] IE browser is no longer supported. v5 uses CSS-in-JS and modern CSS features.

  Modal:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`visible\` renamed to \`open\`
    📝 [BREAKING] Static methods \`Modal.confirm()\` etc. deprecated. Use \`App.useApp()\` hook instead.

  Drawer:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`visible\` renamed to \`open\`
    📝 [BREAKING] Drawer \`style\` and \`className\` now apply to the panel node. Use \`rootStyle\` and \`rootClassName\` for the wrapper.

  Tooltip:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`visible\` renamed to \`open\`

  Popover:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`visible\` renamed to \`open\`

  Popconfirm:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`visible\` renamed to \`open\`

  Dropdown:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`visible\` renamed to \`open\`

  Tag:
    📝 [BREAKING] Prop \`visible\` removed. Use conditional rendering instead.

  Select:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownClassName\` renamed to \`popupClassName\`
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownMatchSelectWidth\` renamed to \`popupMatchSelectWidth\`

  TreeSelect:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownClassName\` renamed to \`popupClassName\`

  Cascader:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownClassName\` renamed to \`popupClassName\`

  AutoComplete:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownClassName\` renamed to \`popupClassName\`

  DatePicker:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownClassName\` renamed to \`popupClassName\`

  TimePicker:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownClassName\` renamed to \`popupClassName\`

  Mentions:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Prop \`dropdownClassName\` renamed to \`popupClassName\`

  Comment:
    📝 [BREAKING] Removed from antd. Use @ant-design/compatible instead.
       Guide: https://ant.design/docs/react/migration-v5

  PageHeader:
    📝 [BREAKING] Removed from antd. Use @ant-design/pro-components instead.
       Guide: https://ant.design/docs/react/migration-v5

  BackTop:
    🔧 [BREAKING] Removed. Use FloatButton.BackTop instead.

  message:
    📝 [BREAKING] Static methods \`message.xxx()\` deprecated. Use \`App.useApp()\` hook instead for context support.
    🔧 [BREAKING] \`message.warn()\` completely removed. Use \`message.warning()\` instead.

  notification:
    📝 [BREAKING] Static methods \`notification.xxx()\` deprecated. Use \`App.useApp()\` hook instead.
    📝 [BREAKING] Static method \`notification.close()\` renamed to \`notification.destroy()\`. Static config options restricted.

  Table:
    📝 [BREAKING] Column \`filterDropdown\` render args changed. \`confirm({ closeDropdown: false })\` replaced by separate \`close\` function.
    🔧 [BREAKING] Column prop \`filterDropdownVisible\` renamed to \`filterDropdownOpen\`.

  Form:
    📝 Prop \`labelCol\` and \`wrapperCol\` can now be set globally via ConfigProvider.

  Slider:
    📝 [BREAKING] Tooltip-related APIs converged into \`tooltip\` property. \`tooltipVisible\` → \`tooltip.open\`, \`tipFormatter\` → \`tooltip.formatter\`, etc.

Total: 34 steps (19 auto-fixable, 15 manual)"
`;

