### \`btn\` deprecated → \`actions\`; \`message\` deprecated → \`title\`.

non-breaking | 📝 manual

**Search pattern:** \`notification\\.(open|success|error|info|warning)\\(\\{[^}]*(\\bbtn\\b|\\bmessage\\b)\`

