### \`Timeline.Item\` deprecated → \`items\`; \`pending\`/\`pendingDot\` deprecated → \`items\`; \`mode=left|right\` → \`mode=start|end\`.

non-breaking | 📝 manual

**Search pattern:** \`(Timeline\\.Item|<Timeline[^>]*\\b(pending|pendingDot|mode\\s*=\\s*['"](?:left|right))\\b)\`

